title: Grateful Dead Live at Madison Square Garden on 1990-09-20
description:
Set 1

Feel Like A Stranger, Althea, It's All Over Now, Ramble On Rose, El Paso, Brown Eyed Women, Greatest Story Ever Told-> U.S. Blues

Set 2

Truckin', China Cat Sunflower-> I Know You Rider, Women Are Smarter, Drums-> Jam-> Dark Star-> Playin' In The Band Reprise-> Dark Star-> Jam-> Throwing Stones-> Touch Of Gray, E: Turn On Your Love Light

reviews.review_text: Wrong This is from naussau collisieum october 1980..... I was there

Not Wrong This is actually exactly what it says it is. Its from 9/20/90. That's Bruce Hornsby throughout but you can definitely tell that's him on "I Know You Rider." No other version sounds quite like this one. It smokes.
